{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-tsx","path":"/interactive-web/","result":{"data":{"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"html":"<h2 id=\"react-three-fiberr3f\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#react-three-fiberr3f\" aria-label=\"react three fiberr3f permalink\" class=\"link-headers before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"https://r3f.docs.pmnd.rs/getting-started/introduction\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">React Three Fiber(R3F)</a></h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>React에서 Three.js를 사용할 수 있게 해주는 Library</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"jsx\"><pre class=\"language-jsx\"><code class=\"language-jsx\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Canvas</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">orthographic</span>\n\t<span class=\"token attr-name\">camera</span><span class=\"token script language-javascript\"><span class=\"token script-punctuation punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token literal-property property\">position</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">100</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token literal-property property\">zoom</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">100</span>\n\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n\t</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mesh</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mesh</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n\t</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>directionalLight</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">intensity</span><span class=\"token script language-javascript\"><span class=\"token script-punctuation punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">position</span><span class=\"token script language-javascript\"><span class=\"token script-punctuation punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Canvas</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;Canvas></code> : 3D Scene 렌더링 기본 컨테이너\n<ul>\n<li>Scene: 오브젝트, 조명, 카메라 배치되는 공간</li>\n<li>perspective : 원근법 / orthographic : 직교법</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;mesh></code> : Three.js 물체 기본 단위</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;directionalLight></code> : 조명\n<ul>\n<li>Ambient Light: 부드러운 전체 조명</li>\n<li>Directional Light: 태양광 강한 그림자</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"react-threedrei\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#react-threedrei\" aria-label=\"react threedrei permalink\" class=\"link-headers before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"https://drei.docs.pmnd.rs/getting-started/introduction\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">@react-three/drei</a></h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>React Three fiber 컴포넌트, 플러그인 패키지<br>\n애니메이션, 조명, 카메라 설정 단순화</p>\n</blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;OrbitControls></code> : 기본 카메라 이동</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;CameraControls></code> : 부드러운 카메라 이동, 정밀한 제어</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;Environment></code> : 내장된 배경 (apartment, city, dawn, forest …)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"https://drei.pmnd.rs/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">drei 컴포넌트 테스트</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"leva\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#leva\" aria-label=\"leva permalink\" class=\"link-headers before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"https://github.com/pmndrs/leva\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">leva</a></h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>설정값 조정 GUI</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"jsx\"><pre class=\"language-jsx\"><code class=\"language-jsx\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> useControls <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"leva\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> materialProps <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">useControls</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t<span class=\"token operator\">...</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"framer-motion\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#framer-motion\" aria-label=\"framer motion permalink\" class=\"link-headers before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"https://motion.dev/docs/react\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Framer Motion</a></h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>React 오픈소스 Animation Library</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3>Framer Componenet</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"jsx\"><pre class=\"language-jsx\"><code class=\"language-jsx\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> motion <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"framer-motion\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>motion.div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">className</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>myClass<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>모든 HTML 및 SVG 요소</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;motion.div></code> <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;motion.span></code> <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;motion.circle></code></li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Framer Componenet Props</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"jsx\"><pre class=\"language-jsx\"><code class=\"language-jsx\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">MyComponent</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">=></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>isValue<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> setIsValue<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">useState</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> someVar <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token function-variable function\">hover</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">isValue</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token literal-property property\">scale</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> isValue<span class=\"token operator\">?</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span> <span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">1.5</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token literal-property property\">reset</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token literal-property property\">scale</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">return</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>motion.div</span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token attr-name\">initial</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>reset<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token attr-name\">whileHover</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>hover<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token attr-name\">variants</span><span class=\"token script language-javascript\"><span class=\"token script-punctuation punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>someVar<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token attr-name\">custom</span><span class=\"token script language-javascript\"><span class=\"token script-punctuation punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>isValue<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token attr-name\">onClick</span><span class=\"token script language-javascript\"><span class=\"token script-punctuation punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token function\">setIsValue</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n\t\t</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>motion.div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>initial: 초기상태\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">x</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">y</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">rotate</code> …</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>animate: 목표위치\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">animate(element, {목표}, {duration})</code><br>\n<code class=\"language-text\">animate(\"div\", {rotate: 90, x: 20 ... }, {duration:0})</code></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>transition: 전환 모습\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">tween</code> : default, <code class=\"language-text\">spring</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">inertia</code></li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">ease</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">delay</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">duration</code></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>variants: 변수, 함수정의 → 객체 반환\n<ul>\n<li>함수 정의 시 하나의 인수 받고 객체 반환할 수 있음</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">custom</code> 통해 prop 전달</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"https://blog.maximeheckel.com/posts/guide-animations-spark-joy-framer-motion/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Framer 튜토리얼</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://motion.dev/examples\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Framer Motion 예제</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"v0\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#v0\" aria-label=\"v0 permalink\" class=\"link-headers before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"https://v0.app/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">v0</a></h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>자연어로 3D 디자인</p>\n</blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>3D Scene 에 Object(Mesh), Camera 생성</li>\n<li>Mesh, Material, 애니메이션, interaction 정의\n<ul>\n<li>Mesh: Object 형태 - spheres, boxes, planes</li>\n<li>Material: 색상, 질감, 반사 속성</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>접근성 제공 (Accessibility)</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">스크린 리더 호환성 위해 대체 텍스트(alt text) 추가</code><br>\n→ <em>어두운 배경 위에 은색 금속 재질의 구체가 중력에 의해 바닥으로 떨어진 뒤 반복적으로 튕기는 인터랙티브 3D 씬입니다. 마우스 드래그로 카메라 각도를 조절하고, 스크롤로 확대 및 축소할 수 있습니다.</em></li>\n</ul>\n<h3>HTML 결합</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\"> ...section 만들고 HTML을 사용해 call to action 버튼 추가</code></li>\n</ul>\n<h3>후처리 효과 추가</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>시각적 품질 높이기\n<ul>\n<li>Bloom, Depth of Field, Motion Blur</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">Apply a bloom effect to the brightest parts of the scene and add depth of field to focus on the main object.</code></li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<p><a href=\"https://blog.olivierlarose.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://blog.olivierlarose.com/</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://vercel.com/blog/add-3d-to-your-web-projects-with-v0-and-react-three-fiber\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://vercel.com/blog/add-3d-to-your-web-projects-with-v0-and-react-three-fiber</a></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Interactive Web","summary":"R3F, Framer Motion","date":"2026.01.25","categories":["Visual UI"],"thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#e8e8e8","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/gatsby-archive/static/f4a91ab9775c1c5ce0812273eccda9cf/47126/interactive-web.png","srcSet":"/gatsby-archive/static/f4a91ab9775c1c5ce0812273eccda9cf/a1453/interactive-web.png 200w,\n/gatsby-archive/static/f4a91ab9775c1c5ce0812273eccda9cf/aeb79/interactive-web.png 400w,\n/gatsby-archive/static/f4a91ab9775c1c5ce0812273eccda9cf/47126/interactive-web.png 800w","sizes":"(min-width: 800px) 800px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/gatsby-archive/static/f4a91ab9775c1c5ce0812273eccda9cf/b6124/interactive-web.webp 200w,\n/gatsby-archive/static/f4a91ab9775c1c5ce0812273eccda9cf/dff21/interactive-web.webp 400w,\n/gatsby-archive/static/f4a91ab9775c1c5ce0812273eccda9cf/b2a35/interactive-web.webp 800w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 800px) 800px, 100vw"}]},"width":800,"height":450}},"publicURL":"/gatsby-archive/static/f4a91ab9775c1c5ce0812273eccda9cf/interactive-web.png"}}}}]}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/interactive-web/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["1463137677"],"slicesMap":{}}